ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : getDefaultsForDestination(\nProfile, DefaultOptions, **destination**)
activate ScanAdapter

note right of ScanAdapter #lightyellow
**Build ScanAttributesCaps (for validation):**
1. createScanAttributesCapsBuilder(Profile, TransmissionMode.JOB)
2. Extract capabilities to validate defaults against
end note

alt destination is HTTP (API 1 default, or API 2 HTTP)
    ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : Create ScanTicketHelper(\n  profile.getBase(), profile.getHttp())
    ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : Extract OptionProfileHelper:\n  helper.getHttpScanOptionsProfileHelper()

    note right of ScanAdapter #lightblue
    **Extract HTTP default options:**
    case HTTP:
      helper = new ScanTicketHelper(profile.getBase(), profile.getHttp());
      return buildScanAttributes(
        helper.getHttpScanOptionsProfileHelper(),
        **defaultOptions.getHttp()**,
        scanAttributesCaps,
        builder);
    end note

    ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : buildScanAttributes(\n  httpProfileHelper,\n  **httpDefaultOptions**,\n  scanAttributesCaps,\n  meBuilder)

else destination is FTP or NETWORK_FOLDER (API 2)
    ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : Create ScanTicketHelper(\n  profile.getBase(), profile.getHttp(),\n  profile.getNetworkFolder())
    ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : Extract OptionProfileHelper:\n  helper.getNetworkFolderScanOptionsProfileHelper()

    note right of ScanAdapter #lightgreen
    **Extract NetworkFolder default options:**
    case FTP:
    case NETWORK_FOLDER:
      helper = new ScanTicketHelper(
        profile.getBase(),
        profile.getHttp(),
        profile.getNetworkFolder());
      return buildScanAttributes(
        helper.getNetworkFolderScanOptionsProfileHelper(),
        **defaultOptions.getNetworkFolder()**,
        scanAttributesCaps,
        builder);
    end note

    ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : buildScanAttributes(\n  networkFolderProfileHelper,\n  **networkFolderDefaultOptions**,\n  scanAttributesCaps,\n  meBuilder)

else destination is ME, EMAIL, or USB (API 2)
        ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : <color:red><b>Create ScanTicketHelper(\n  profile.getBase(), profile.getHttp(),\n  profile.getNetworkFolder(), profile.getJobStorage())</b></color>
        ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : <color:red><b>Extract OptionProfileHelper:\n  helper.getJobStorageScanOptionsProfileHelper()</b></color>

        note right of ScanAdapter #pink
        <color:red><b>**Extract JobStorage default options:**</b></color>
        <color:red><b>case ME:
        case EMAIL:
        case USB:
          helper = new ScanTicketHelper(
            profile.getBase(),
            profile.getHttp(),
            profile.getNetworkFolder(),
            profile.getJobStorage());
          return buildScanAttributes(
            helper.getJobStorageScanOptionsProfileHelper(),
            **defaultOptions.getJobStorage()**,
            scanAttributesCaps,
            builder);</b></color>
        end note

        ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : buildScanAttributes(\n  jobStorageProfileHelper,\n  <color:red><b>jobStorageDefaultOptions</b></color>,\n  scanAttributesCaps,\n  meBuilder)

end

activate ScanAdapter

note right of ScanAdapter #lightyellow
**Convert E2 DefaultOptions → ScanAttributes:**
For each scan option in DefaultOptions:
1. Check if option is available in Profile
   - optionProfileHelper.getOptionDefinition(name).getIsAvailable()
2. Convert E2 type → Workpath API type using **ScanTypeMapping**
3. Set converted value to MeBuilder

**Mapped options (20+ options):**
- colorMode, resolution, duplex (plexMode + bindingFormat)
- scanSize, orientation, scanPreview
- backgroundCleanup, contrast, sharpness
- blankPageSuppression, captureMode
- documentFormat, fileTransmissionMode
- mediaSource, misfeedDetection
- outputQuality, progressDialogMode
- textPhotoOptimization, automaticStraighten
- fileName (if explicit)
end note

ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : Set each default option:\n- setColorMode()\n- setResolution()\n- setDuplex()\n- setScanSize()\n- etc. (20+ options)

note right of ScanAdapter #white
**Example conversions (destination-specific):**

**HTTP defaults:**
E2: resolution = 300 → Workpath: 300
E2: colorMode = "color" → Workpath: ColorMode.COLOR

**NetworkFolder defaults:**
E2: resolution = 200 → Workpath: 200
E2: colorMode = "grayscale" → Workpath: ColorMode.GRAYSCALE

// Different destinations may have different defaults!
end note

ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : builder.build(scanAttributesCaps)
note right of ScanAdapter #pink
**Validation against capabilities**
Ensures default values are within
device's supported capabilities
end note

ScanAdapter --> ScanAdapter : Return ScanAttributes
deactivate ScanAdapter
deactivate ScanAdapter

ScanAdapter -> ScanAdapter : JsonParser.toJson(ScanAttributes)
ScanAdapter --> ScanCP : Return Json String\n(ScanAttributes)
deactivate ScanAdapter

ScanCP -[#0000FF]-> lib : <<IPC>>\n Return Bundle
deactivate ScanCP
note left of ScanCP #white
**Response Bundle:**
{"resultCode": -1,
 "result": ScanAttributes Json String }
end note

lib -> lib : JsonParser.fromJson(jsonStr, ScanAttributes.class)
lib --> User : Return\nScanAttributes
deactivate lib

